exceptions.exn: In environment u : nat -> R Unable to unify "(is_inf_seq (fun n : nat => Rbar_opp (?M2370 n)) (Rbar_opp ?M2371) -> is_sup_seq ?M2370 ?M2371) /\\ (is_sup_seq ?M2370 ?M2371 -> is_inf_seq (fun n : nat => Rbar_opp (?M2370 n)) (Rbar_opp ?M2371))" with "match Rbar_opp (Sup_seq (fun m : nat => Inf_seq (fun n : nat => u (n + m)%nat))) with | Finite l => forall eps : posreal, (forall N : nat, exists n : nat, (N <= n)%nat /\\ l - eps < (fun n0 : nat => - u n0) n) /\\ (exists N : nat, forall n : nat, (N <= n)%nat -> (fun n0 : nat => - u n0) n < l + eps) | p_infty => forall (M : R) (N : nat), exists n : nat, (N <= n)%nat /\\ M < (fun n0 : nat => - u n0) n | m_infty => forall M : R, exists N : nat, forall n : nat, (N <= n)%nat -> (fun n0 : nat => - u n0) n < M end".
